Exchange Monitoring:

How to get the counter IDS 
regedit: HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows NT\CurrentVersion\Perflib\009\Counter
The id is the number befor the name.
or with lodctr

----------------------------------------------------------------------
counters = 111111:msx_dc_access
MSExchange ADAccess Domain Controllers
----------------------------------------------------------------------
counters = 11111:msx_dumpster
MSExchangeTransport Dumpster
----------------------------------------------------------------------
counters = 68312:msx_queued_mailbox
MSExchangeIS Mailbox
----------------------------------------------------------------------
counters = 64848:msx_activesync
MSExchange ActiveSync
----------------------------------------------------------------------
counters = 66210:msx_rpc_clientaccess
MSExchange RpcClientAccess
----------------------------------------------------------------------
counters = 66804:msx_db_reads_avg_latency
MSExchange Database
